Software Design Resources — OKF viewer
=======================================

A self-contained, offline, no-dependency faceted browser for this OKF bundle.
`scripts/build_viewer.py` walks the bundle and inlines the data plus
`viewer/app.css` and `viewer/app.js` into a single `dist/index.html`.

Design & approach were inspired by:
  - Google's Open Knowledge Format (OKF) reference viewer
    https://github.com/GoogleCloudPlatform/knowledge-catalog
  - The Repodo monorepo's `tools/okf` viewer (walk -> inline -> detail-panel pattern)

No third-party code is vendored in this v1: there is no CDN dependency, no
bundled cytoscape/marked, and no graph view. Card bodies are rendered by a
small inline Markdown renderer in app.js. A relationship graph is a planned
follow-up.
